<!--
  SITEMAP GUIDELINES:
  ===================
  
  1. PRIORITY VALUES:
     - 1.0: Homepage
     - 0.8-0.9: Main category pages, important products
     - 0.6-0.7: Regular products, blog posts
     - 0.4-0.5: Policy pages, less important content
  
  2. CHANGEFREQ OPTIONS:
     - always: Real-time content (rare for e-commerce)
     - hourly: Frequently updated content
     - daily: Products with price changes, homepage
     - weekly: Regular products, collections
     - monthly: Static pages, old blog posts
     - yearly: Archived content
     - never: Never changes
  
  3. IMAGE SITEMAP EXTENSION:
     - Include up to 1,000 images per URL
     - Use descriptive titles and captions
     - Images must be accessible to crawlers
  
  4. SUBMISSION:
     - Submit to Google Search Console
     - Submit to Bing Webmaster Tools
     - Reference in robots.txt
  
  5. LIMITS:
     - Max 50,000 URLs per sitemap
     - Max 50MB uncompressed
     - Use sitemap index for larger sites
-->
